---

### Group Membership Purpose

| Group Name | Role Purpose |
|------------|--------------|
| GG-Management | Administrative oversight, higher-level permissions |
| GG-HR | Sensitive employee records and HR-related access |
| GG-Sales | Client, CRM, and sales-specific resources |
| GG-IT-Support | Technical support responsibilities, IT tools, remote access |

These Global Security Groups will be used in future milestones to assign **permissions**, **folder access**, and **Group Policy Objects (GPO)** based on role-based access control (RBAC).

